  47,19,"So, know Ëąwell, O Prophet,Ëş that there is no god Ëąworthy of worshipËş except Allah. And seek forgiveness for your shortcomingsÂ and for Ëąthe sins ofËş the believing men and women. For Allah ËąfullyËş knows your movements and places of rest ËąO peopleËş"
  47,20,"And the believers say, â€śIf only a sĂ»rahÂ was revealed Ëąallowing self-defenceËş!â€ť Yet when a precise sĂ»rahÂ is revealed, in which fighting is ËąexplicitlyËş mentioned, you see those with sickness in their hearts staring at you like someone in the throes of death. It would have been better for them"
